      "content": "i don't want a story. i don't want a glimmer of hope. that's just more fiction. the reality is that the person i was is gone, and the person left behind is just a shell. it feels like the only honest thing left to do is stop trying to pretend. it feels like everything is just... finished. like the curtain should just come down.",
